Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.45,0:01:49.08,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a bad feeling about this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:53.75,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Father! I brought a sacrifice!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.75,0:01:56.34,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,"Father"? So suddenly...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.90,0:02:01.85,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:08.84,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.60,0:02:45.78,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Envy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.45,0:02:47.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Envy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.85,0:02:48.92,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,This is him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.86,0:02:52.69,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.08,0:02:57.23,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:00.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:04.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al in the armor... which means...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.08,0:03:08.99,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.43,0:03:10.33,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:11.40,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:12.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.60,0:03:13.25,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.25,0:03:16.21,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad to see you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.41,0:03:14.33,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts, Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.33,0:03:16.71,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Your armor's hurting me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:24.01,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that I'm so glad to see you're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.67,0:03:28.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.55,0:03:29.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:33.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,For worrying you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:41.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But where the heck are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.03,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.03,0:03:45.36,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Humans came out of his stomach?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:49.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hohen...heim?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.95,0:03:53.52,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,An arm and a leg made of steel, and a suit of armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:59.59,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Are you the Elric Brothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,It's not him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.66,0:04:05.24,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Are you mistaking me for somebody?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.24,0:04:06.97,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.97,0:04:08.97,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Hohen...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:13.49,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you're talking about Van Hohenheim?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:15.73,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What is your relationship with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:18.98,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He's... our dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.78,0:04:23.23,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.23,0:04:27.70,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What a surprise! He ended up having kids?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:36.54,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,But aren't your last names Elric?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.54,0:04:38.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Elric is our mother's maiden name!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.25,0:04:40.66,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.08,0:04:43.27,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,So, where is he now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.27,0:04:44.69,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hell if I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.69,0:04:47.05,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly, who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.05,0:04:48.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You look just like Hohenheim!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:51.17,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way he'd die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:53.66,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,And he's even had kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.25,0:04:51.61,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.61,0:04:53.17,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, this man is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:57.40,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're injured?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:59.56,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,And you're missing your left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.49,0:05:06.32,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.24,0:05:07.41,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.41,0:05:09.25,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,A broken bone, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.00,0:05:19.04,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's fixed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.41,0:05:22.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:24.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Oww!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.72,0:05:26.57,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Now for your ribs.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.43,0:05:35.00,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You two are important to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.00,0:05:37.06,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be too reckless with your bodies, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:41.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He used alchemy without a single hand motion.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.77,0:05:44.03,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,And he didn't make the rest of my armor thinner, either...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.90,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, it's not equivalent exchange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.90,0:05:48.91,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:51.91,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,It's unreal! How could your insides be in such a state?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.66,0:05:55.55,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to ask you the same exact question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.55,0:05:56.91,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.92,0:06:01.64,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You can eat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.64,0:06:02.69,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.69,0:06:03.84,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hang on!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.84,0:06:06.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He's my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.00,0:06:09.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a human sacrifice, so don't kill him for my sake. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.30,0:06:11.38,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,That's not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.38,0:06:14.53,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,He's useless to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.53,0:06:15.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:20.26,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, the Homunculi call him "Father".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.26,0:06:22.54,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who created them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.54,0:06:23.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:25.92,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Even though he patched us up...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.92,0:06:28.03,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.00,0:06:30.63,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Your attitude...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:34.16,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as those who laugh at humans for being foolish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:39.21,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Do you consider insects crawling about the Earth to be foolish?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.69,0:06:46.36,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Even if insects struggle, the difference between you and them is so great that you don't exactly give a damn.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:51.47,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,That's precisely how I feel about you humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.25,0:06:59.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I appreciate you healing our wounds,\Nbut I don't think I can get along with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.34,0:07:01.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you're the cause of everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.90,0:07:04.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of you quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:06.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be worrying about the small fry!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:09.11,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're calling me small fry now, runt?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:11.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Runt?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.40,0:07:18.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've got their leader!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.72,0:07:32.91,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Ling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:35.72,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:41.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How can he use alchemy without a single hand motion?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.47,0:07:46.27,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,What a waste of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:22.02,Default,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We can't use alchemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.51,0:08:24.40,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Ed! Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.50,0:08:31.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What did that geezer do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.45,0:08:32.32,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:34.86,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we use alchemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.02,0:08:40.37,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, these tiny beings are unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.37,0:08:43.92,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,They start to think they're at the top of the world as soon as they gain some power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.92,0:08:46.21,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,They don't even know what exactly they're using.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:52.71,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really think all this prosperity was created with the powers of humans only?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.71,0:08:55.93,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,How laughable, fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.86,0:08:59.56,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.56,0:09:02.53,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You promised you'd tell me as soon as we got out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:03.70,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:07.84,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,I don't remember making promises with you insects.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:08.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.51,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You're talking too much, Envy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.51,0:09:12.71,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:17.61,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,He could be good for the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.36,0:09:22.52,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I may be able to create another pawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.74,0:09:29.00,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,That's... a philosopher's stone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.14,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.54,0:09:32.37,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,So you're planning to do it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:33.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Do what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.39,0:09:35.76,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He's creating a Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.13,0:09:40.11,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He's going to inject the philosopher's stone into him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:43.97,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,If all goes well, a homunculus with a human base will be complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.06,0:09:52.57,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Well, most humans end up dying because they aren't capable of fighting the stone's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:54.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'll let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.05,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Let go, Envy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.05,0:10:00.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.45,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't we use alchemy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:05.34,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.34,0:10:06.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Geezer! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:09.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He has people waiting for his return!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.55,0:10:11.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:18.72,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Humans can't shoot me if I do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.56,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:23.00,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.00,0:10:24.41,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! Don't shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:27.38,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Don't interfere.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:28.56,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,This is fine by me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:29.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:32.80,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I came to this country looking for a philosopher's stone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.80,0:10:35.26,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,And he's just going to give it to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.84,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly what I wished for!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.84,0:10:38.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell are you saying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.19,0:10:40.70,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Sounds interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.45,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Then as you wish, it's all yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.37,0:10:46.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.50,0:10:56.30,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ling!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.91,0:11:00.10,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I... I told you not...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.10,0:11:01.94,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,...to interfere!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.87,0:11:10.61,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine... Just wait for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:15.18,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the man who will become the Emperor of Xing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.18,0:11:16.48,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,...Ling Yao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:39.30,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is a brat doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:41.27,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:43.25,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have your body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.25,0:11:44.97,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put it to good use.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.65,0:11:47.26,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.26,0:11:49.47,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,It's all yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.47,0:11:50.50,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:53.10,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that I'll accept you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.10,0:11:55.10,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't people normally be against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.10,0:11:57.66,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to become the Emperor of Xing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.66,0:12:02.70,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,How do you expect me to do that if I can't even accept a few dozen people in my body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.88,0:12:07.38,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I like decisive guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.38,0:12:09.35,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,But you'd better not regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.35,0:12:11.08,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Regret?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.08,0:12:17.09,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,If I return empty-handed, how could I possibly face my servant who cut her own arm off to save me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.45,0:12:20.99,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I want power...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:26.12,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,Absolute power that will help me protect and gain more!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.12,0:12:27.97,Default,Ling,0000,0000,0000,,I knew the risks from the beginning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.63,0:12:32.01,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I like your greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.01,0:12:36.77,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, show me how prepared you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.18,0:12:48.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.85,0:12:53.27,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh, the guy who owned this body?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:57.88,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but now it belongs to me, Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.95,0:13:01.00,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Not Ling, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:02.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Greed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.45,0:13:14.22,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're that Greed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:17.84,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by "that" Greed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.84,0:13:19.41,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You don't remember?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.41,0:13:20.91,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,The one at Dublith...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.91,0:13:23.11,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, so what Greed are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.11,0:13:25.85,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,The Greed that came before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.85,0:13:28.24,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.78,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Well, as you can see,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.78,0:13:33.16,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a different Greed from the one you guys know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.61,0:13:34.86,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to Ling?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.08,0:13:38.30,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He was an interesting brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.30,0:13:40.92,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He accepted me in a matter of seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.19,0:13:45.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No way! There's no way he's that easy to take control of!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:48.09,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me! Ling!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ling!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.68,0:14:03.00,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.00,0:14:04.15,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.71,0:14:06.40,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.40,0:14:09.53,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,He's a person, but at the same time, he's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.97,0:14:14.99,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, a lot of these guys aren't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.34,0:14:18.53,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Shao May!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.53,0:14:20.54,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad to see you're safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:22.43,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any idea how worried I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.04,0:14:26.55,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, I don't really get it, but is this some tearful reunion?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.00,0:14:33.90,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,It seems they aren't working together with the Homunculi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.44,0:14:36.49,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.49,0:14:37.85,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.85,0:14:40.08,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Sir Edward?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:41.07,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.76,0:14:44.98,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see him anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.98,0:14:46.61,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pointing right at him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:50.11,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,That small one is the Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:12.10,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,You toyed with my pure heart, you midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.10,0:15:13.93,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Speak for yourself, midget!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.36,0:15:17.66,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,He's the Ishbalan I didn't get to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.93,0:15:20.57,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,The disobedient people, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.57,0:15:26.15,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,He's the one who uses destructive alchemy and continues to interfere with our plans, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:17.11,Default-alt,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do to her, Brother?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.11,0:15:18.73,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't do a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.15,0:15:28.63,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Take care of them, Gluttony.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:31.38,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,He can't use alchemy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.38,0:15:33.37,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:39.37,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:40.96,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never forgive you!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:45.17,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,You stepped all over a maiden's heart,\Nand on top of that, you kidnapped Shao May!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.59,0:15:48.60,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Divine punishment...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.60,0:15:50.10,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,...for all of you!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.96,0:15:55.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.50,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,We still can't use it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.50,0:16:02.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.70,0:16:05.86,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,How can you two use alchemy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:08.36,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:11.72,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:13.43,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,How can Scar and that little girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.43,0:16:14.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.48,0:16:16.12,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,No idea, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:19.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This could be our chance to fill them in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.13,0:16:20.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:25.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you the truth behind the Ishbal rebellion!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.14,0:16:27.58,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,The truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.58,0:16:30.55,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,The death of the child which became the trigger of the rebellion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:35.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...was caused by him, disguised as a military officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.93,0:16:40.16,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They're behind it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.80,0:16:53.86,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like I'll have to ask you to explain this in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.72,0:17:03.29,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.62,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Why did my people have to fall?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:11.59,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on your answer, I'll send you to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.59,0:17:12.63,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.63,0:17:16.78,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,I won't send you to God, where my fellow Ishbalans reside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:20.20,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Think of yourselves as undeserving of eternal rest or redemption!!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:29.21,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.21,0:17:31.35,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad for a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.35,0:17:34.45,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Greed, get rid of the intruders.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.45,0:17:35.68,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:44.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to believe it, Ling!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.73,0:17:48.17,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.38,0:17:55.39,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.39,0:17:58.75,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Could that be Ling from the Yao clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.72,0:18:01.76,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,A little girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.92,0:18:04.77,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Soft body!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.21,0:18:13.90,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Hey you, how can you use alchemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.28,0:18:20.66,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you really are using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.28,0:18:24.02,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Human destruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:26.20,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,No, decomposition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.89,0:18:35.80,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,A second later, and I would have been...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.77,0:18:38.09,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Scar!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.29,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,Shao May... Run...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.93,0:18:48.94,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,You're mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.65,0:18:51.66,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.11,0:18:59.40,Default,May,0000,0000,0000,,I never asked you to save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:01.44,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.44,0:19:04.41,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,They're ruthless toward humans who are of no benefit to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.04,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.76,0:19:11.35,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,There's way too many of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.65,0:19:18.76,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,You two didn't run away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.94,0:19:29.18,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Scar, could you take this girl and get out of here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.80,0:19:32.01,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to let me escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.01,0:19:35.27,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I killed those doctors...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:38.51,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I want to beat the hell out of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:41.53,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,To be honest, I don't even want to ask you for any favors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.53,0:19:44.29,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,But right now, it's more important to take this girl somewhere safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:46.47,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,What will you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:53.37,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, my brother and I are important to them in some way.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.37,0:19:56.88,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we stay here, they won't kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.67,0:20:02.45,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, I won't be able to protect\Nthat girl and escape from here at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:06.05,Default,Scar,0000,0000,0000,,And I don't have the slightest intention of running away, either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.93,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,He decomposed water?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.61,0:20:23.47,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, let me know before you do stuff like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.47,0:20:25.11,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,How reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:30.96,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Igniting hydrogen? That's clever of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.28,0:20:34.54,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Where is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.54,0:20:36.58,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:37.67,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:40.13,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Gluttony, track him by scent!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.34,0:20:45.98,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You're out of lives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.98,0:20:47.45,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,You've died too much!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:51.99,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That was a nice kick.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.99,0:20:54.64,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I think this'll be more fun than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.40,0:20:58.32,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.32,0:21:00.72,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Come back to your senses!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.72,0:21:01.59,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.59,0:21:02.54,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.54,0:21:04.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Give Ling back his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.37,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,No can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.09,0:21:13.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.92,0:21:15.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do about your country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.65,0:21:17.58,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What about Lan Fan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:29.51,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Father! I got him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:29.51,Default-alt,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow! Ow! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:33.20,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Take him upstairs, where Wrath is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.07,0:21:38.56,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously... Always screwing around with us...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.56,0:21:43.40,Default,Envy,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you guys behave, we won't do a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:45.69,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.53,0:21:48.65,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:50.43,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Ling...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.03,0:21:52.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,...is inside of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.51,0:23:33.45,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,You used up your regeneration abilities, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.93,0:23:36.85,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,Worry not, my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.99,0:23:52.60,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,I will recreate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.60,0:23:54.74,Default,Father,0000,0000,0000,,With your memories, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.70,0:24:03.58,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Humans in chaos, struggle and writhe in agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.58,0:24:06.46,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Because that serves as proof that one is alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.08,0:24:11.34,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,And struggle and kneel before me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.97,0:24:16.47,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.47,0:24:20.47,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 29, The Fool's Struggle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.05,0:24:25.78,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Will the man who had his limbs twisted be able to stand again?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.78,0:24:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
